snippet.textDisplay: Aeri aali piya bin sounds totally out of place in this song...  It is very difficult to fit in a bandish in Yaman in a composition like this. If they were trying to get the folksy feel they should have kept to the folk bandishes. Good performances by the individual artists but that bandish in the middle sounded too random which is sad because it is such an awesome bandish and has there have been renditions by so many of the greats in Hindustani Classical...
